\v 16 \x - \xo 16:16 \xt Jenesis 12:7; 26:3\x*An Abraham ko Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam gami. 
\q2 Egha Aisak koma Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam ak…®ri. 
