\v 17 \x - \xo 16:17-18 \xt Jenesis 28:13\x*An Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam Jekop koma a gami, a Israelian ovavim, 
\q2 egha Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam gavgavim a gan…®ngi, eght…® a zurara ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam. 
\b  
\q1  
\v 18 Ikiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® Kenan…®n nguazim n…® dan…®ngam, 
\q2 eght…® nguazir kam n…®n ovavir boribar nguazim…®n ikiam.‚Äù 
\b  
\q1  
\v 19 Fom…®ra Israelia bar av…®rasemezir puvat…®gha, 
\q2 Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibar m…®n pura Kenan…®n nguazim…®n iti. 
\q1  
\v 20 Egha Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizibar m…®n pura tintinibar dagh aruav…®ra iti. 
\q1  
\v 21 \x - \xo 16:21-22 \xt Jenesis 20:3-7\x*Ez…® God tarazi ataghiz…®, me me m…®sogha me ab…®nizir puvat…®. 
\q2 A men akurvagha me bagha atrivir maba akar gavgaviba me gan…®ga atriviba d…®kab…®ra, 
