\v 22 \x - \xo 16:22 \xt Onger Akaba 105:15\x*egha ghaze, ‚ÄúK…® ua bagha m…®sevezir gumazamiziba, ia me gas…®ghas…®ghan mark…®! 
\q2 Ia nan akam inigha izir gumaziba paz…® me damuan mark…®!‚Äù 
\b  
\q1  
\v 23 Nguazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh onger akabar amu. 
\q2 Dughiabar zurara ia an gun uariv m…®k…®m suam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God zurara en akurvasi. 
